<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/styles.css">
    <title>Library - About</title>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="about-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Library, your ultimate destination for books and reading!</p>

            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h3>Our Story</h3>
                    <p>Library was founded with a passion for books and a mission to make reading accessible to everyone. We believe that books have the power to inspire, educate, and transform lives. That's why we have curated a vast collection of books across various genres and topics to cater to the diverse interests of our readers.</p>
                    <p>Our team of dedicated book lovers works tirelessly to bring you the best reading experience possible. From classic literature to contemporary bestsellers, we have something for every book enthusiast. We are committed to providing a user-friendly platform where you can easily discover, explore, and immerse yourself in the world of books.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="assets/about-image.png" alt="About Image">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="about-features">
                <div class="feature">
                    <i class="fas fa-book"></i>
                    <h4>Extensive Collection</h4>
                    <p>Explore our vast collection of books spanning various genres and topics.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="feature">
                    <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                    <h4>Easy Search</h4>
                    <p>Find your favorite books quickly and easily with our intuitive search functionality.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="feature">
                    <i class="fas fa-tablet-alt"></i>
                    <h4>Mobile-Friendly</h4>
                    <p>Access our library on the go with our mobile-friendly website.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="assets/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>